name: BlockCity | B03H01 | Commodore Living
description:
Calling the rents overpriced would be a mean exaggeration for this beautifully designed architectural wonder. However, some people argue that it has been inspired heavily by a well-known piece of computer hardware from pre-colonial earth.

Own a 12-second turntable of your 3D-rendered meta real estate - visit BlockCity: https://rtz23.de/blockcity/?b=3
